{"tid":2070179,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"程鼎一：推出深度遊攻略鼓勵本地遊 未來兩周宣布優惠","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T03:18:43.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4cd402e7c9a9a35d9d02299da96fd2e68b7aab","tid":2070179,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"程鼎一：推出深度遊攻略鼓勵本地遊 未來兩周宣布優惠<br />\n2020-06-19 HKT 10:12<br />\n<br />\n旅遊發展局總幹事程鼎一預計，今年與明年訪港旅客分別會少於高峰期的一半，即3000多萬人次以下，他認為本港應趁機改善接待旅客能力及質素。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局近日推出「深度旅遊」攻略，鼓勵市民參加本地遊。程鼎一接受本台訪問時說，近年訪港旅客量很多，大家像習慣生意「唔憂做」，亦有市民嫌旅客太多。他說趁旅遊業低迷，可讓市民做自己的「遊客」，更了解香港後，發現好的景點，日後亦會做好的主人，招待訪港旅客。他透露預計未來兩星期會宣布，以零售、飲食消費換取本地團的優惠。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532935-20200619.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532935-20200619.htm&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C25pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=309feac6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532935-20200619.htm&h=685c81c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532935-20200619.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「隱世小島」應該是指類似南北果洲果類地方<br />\n難以想像那些荒島將會人山人海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f503660e5b0bf2e92ca876c7fe7f46931c393d39","tid":2070179,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:05:09.000Z","msg":"等看隱世小島<br />\n多人過旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f958e65db750555924d10e390284671efe78302","tid":2070179,"uid":53515,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:09:30.000Z","msg":"之前就搵公園起樓，拆哂香港特色建築街道發展<br />\n<br />\n依家就叫人去荒島旅遊，依個政府算吧啦"},{"pid":"fb5775ded1ea20bc9284d160e8489593186e4fe7","tid":2070179,"uid":20170,"like":0,"dislike"